# Air Temperature Prediction using LSTM, GRU, CNN-LSTM

## Description
This project predicts air temperature using deep learning models like LSTM, GRU, and CNN-LSTM.

## Features
- Time series forecasting
- RMSE evaluation
- Multiple model comparison

## Tools Used
- Python
- TensorFlow/Keras
- NumPy, Pandas

## Results
Achieved RMSE of ~1.2
